Internet. I have some home internet connection which is slow and expensive. My ISP charges for phone line, which I don't even have wired, and then for 2GB of traffic, which is basically nothing. I thought well there is no way around it, my choices are horrible, except I recently realized that I need to travel to get some time on some sites, sometimes there is no other choice, modem type which can be attached to terminal, which is pretty cool, because it's cheaper, but in the end it's the same slow internet I can get at home. Perhaps I am surrounded with too crappy options that I am feeling such like I need to rebel. Perhaps my options are available to you, so my adhoc solutions are not an option.^1

I recently asked Ubercart vendors to allows VR images to be uploaded to description, it was not planned, Slovensko Sopot was not in my mind when I was uploading a bunch of items.3 This morning I woke up and in my paypal is pending payment. We have our first order! That's wonderful, because I did not expect any early transactions on our site! I did expect some transactions, but expect them different. It's great thing that everything is fine.
